    • Method Detail

      • create

        public static Session create(android.content.Context context,
             Clock clock,
             java.lang.Integer campaignID,
             java.lang.Integer messageId)
        Creates a session with the same session number and start time, and returns it. If this is the first session being created, it will increment the session and use the current time.
        Parameters:
        context - The app context.
        clock - The clock used to create a start time if required.
        campaignID - The ID for the campaign that the session will be associated with.
        messageId - The ID for the message that the session will be associated with.
        Returns:
        A session with the same number and start time as the previous session.

      • incrementAndCreate

        public static Session incrementAndCreate(android.content.Context context,
                         Clock clock,
                         java.lang.Integer campaignID,
                         java.lang.Integer messageId)
        Creates a session with the current time as the start time and the previous session number + 1 as the session number. If this is the first session being created, it will increment off the SESSION_NUM_BASE_OFFSET.
        Parameters:
        context - The app context.
        clock - The clock used to create a start time.
        campaignID - The ID for the campaign that the session will be associated with.
        messageId - The ID for the message that the session will be associated with.
        Returns:
        A session with a session number one higher than the previous session number.
